{"tid":1517841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家睇清楚 呢個自稱自由文明既社會發生咩事？","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:08:45.000Z","uid":84396,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8b99e31bc8fb1d628990cce316180228e8d58a","tid":1517841,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:54:53.000Z","msg":"岑子杰，民陣召集人，遇襲；<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天，民族黨召集人，被捕；<br />\n<br />\n鍾健平，元朗遊行發起人，遇襲；<br />\n<br />\n劉穎匡，觀塘遊行發起人，被捕；<br />\n<br />\n梁金成，上水遊行發起人，遇襲；<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志黃之鋒、周庭，被捕；<br />\n<br />\n學生動源召集人鍾翰林，遇襲。<br />\n<br />\n許銳宇，沙田區議員，被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪好撚荒謬<br />\n<br />\n申請合法集會遊行 出反對通知書都夠仆街 依家仲要叫班黑打人<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪好撚嬲？我都好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所以唔該大家唔好縮<br />\n<br />\n聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n推返啲集結post上黎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNOARUw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNOARUw.jpg&h=6f547a40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d170625137ebe261d15060b136bf7f01a4acc200","tid":1517841,"uid":84396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288b2d803b048fc2b73a9a83f7ea7bdc2a2d22b7","tid":1517841,"uid":843